---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import site from '@/lib/site';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Myers' Cocktail IV Therapy | Menon Medispa | Millburn, NJ"
  description="The Myers' Cocktail IV therapy in Millburn NJ. The original, time-tested vitamin drip for overall wellness, energy, and immune support."
>
  <main class="sp" data-slug="myers-cocktail-iv-therapy">

    <section class="sp-hero" aria-label="The Myers' Cocktail IV Therapy">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div class="sp-hero__grid">
          <div class="sp-hero__content">
            <h1 class="sp-hero__title">The Myers' Cocktail IV Therapy</h1>
            <p class="sp-hero__eyebrow">The Original All-In-One Wellness IV Drip.</p>
            <p class="sp-hero__lead">The Myers' Cocktail is the original IV vitamin therapy, developed by Dr. John Myers in the 1960s. This time-tested, all-in-one formula remains the gold standard for supporting overall wellness, enhancing energy, and restoring balance.</p>
            <div class="sp-hero__actions">
              <a class="sp-btn sp-btn--gold" href="/consultation">Book Your IV Therapy</a>
            </div>
            <div class="sp-reviews">
              <div class="sp-reviews__avatars">
                <img src="/images/90411e0041df.png" alt="Client review" width="44" height="44" />
                <img src="/images/305afeda5f9a.png" alt="Client review" width="44" height="44" />
                <img src="/images/b95880091b44.png" alt="Client review" width="44" height="44" />
              </div>
              <div class="sp-reviews__text">
                <span class="sp-reviews__stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</span>
                <span class="sp-reviews__count">100+ 5 Star Reviews</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <img class="sp-hero__img" src="/images/651c7c197b52.png" alt="The Myers' Cocktail IV Therapy" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-badges" aria-label="Highlights">
      <div class="sp-container sp-badges__row">
        <p class="sp-badge"><span class="sp-badge__check">&#10003;</span> The Original IV Therapy</p>
        <p class="sp-badge"><span class="sp-badge__check">&#10003;</span> Comprehensive Wellness</p>
        <p class="sp-badge"><span class="sp-badge__check">&#10003;</span> Clinically Proven</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-plain" aria-label="Formulas">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;">
          <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(1.75rem,3vw,2.25rem);color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 1.5rem;">Choose Your Formula</h2>
          <div style="background:#f8f4f0;padding:1.5rem;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
            <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-xl);color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.4rem;">Myers' Cocktail</h3>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);font-style:italic;color:#6a6470;margin:0 0 0.75rem;font-size:var(--text-sm);">The gold standard for overall health, energy, and wellness restoration.</p>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0 0 0.75rem;line-height:1.7;">The Myers' Cocktail delivers a comprehensive blend of vitamins and minerals that work synergistically to support your body's most fundamental functions.</p>
            <ul style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;line-height:1.8;padding-left:1.5rem;margin:0;"><li>Magnesium: A critical mineral involved in over 300 enzymatic reactions, helping to reduce fatigue, relieve muscle tension, and support cardiovascular health.</li><li>Calcium: Works with Magnesium for optimal muscle function and nerve transmission.</li><li>B-Vitamins (B12, B5, B6, B-Complex): A comprehensive blend essential for energy metabolism, nerve function, and red blood cell production.</li><li>Vitamin C: A high-dose antioxidant boost that supports immune function, collagen production, and overall cellular health.</li></ul>
          </div>
          <p style="margin-top:2rem;"><a class="sp-btn sp-btn--gold" href="/consultation">Schedule Now</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-photos" aria-label="Customer Photos">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div class="sp-photos__head"><h2>Hear From Our Customers!</h2></div>
        <div class="sp-photos__grid">
          <img src="/images/9ebaca3843d3.jpg" alt="IV Therapy customer" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/images/6c461885a28e.jpg" alt="IV Therapy customer" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/images/823792ea5ead.jpg" alt="IV Therapy customer" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/images/cd675890fe0d.jpg" alt="IV Therapy customer" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/images/2e5d1e68225a.jpg" alt="IV Therapy customer" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-plain sp-plain--alt" aria-label="Process">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;">
          <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(1.75rem,3vw,2.25rem);color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 1.5rem;">Simple, Relaxing, and Effective</h2>
          <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem;">
            <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;">
              <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-2xl);color:var(--color-accent-warm);flex-shrink:0;line-height:1;">01</span>
              <div><h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.25rem;">Personalized Consultation</h3><p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0;line-height:1.7;">Your session begins with a brief consultation with one of our registered nurses. They will review your wellness goals and answer any questions to ensure your treatment is perfectly suited to your needs.</p></div>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;">
              <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-2xl);color:var(--color-accent-warm);flex-shrink:0;line-height:1;">02</span>
              <div><h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.25rem;">Relax and Recharge</h3><p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0;line-height:1.7;">Once settled in our comfortable therapy lounge, the IV drip is administered. The process is virtually painless and takes about 45-60 minutes. You can relax, read, or catch up on emails while your body absorbs the nutrients.</p></div>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;">
              <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-2xl);color:var(--color-accent-warm);flex-shrink:0;line-height:1;">03</span>
              <div><h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.25rem;">Feel the Benefits</h3><p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0;line-height:1.7;">Many clients report immediate benefits after their session. The nutrients continue to work for days, supporting your body's natural processes and helping you feel and look your best.</p></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-pricing" aria-label="Pricing">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div class="sp-pricing__head">
          <h2>Book Your IV Therapy</h2>
          <p style="font-style:italic;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">All IV Drips are 500ml. Upgrade to 1000ml for only $25</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sp-pricelist">
          <div class="sp-priceitem">
            <img class="sp-priceitem__thumb" src="/images/651c7c197b52.png" alt="Myers' Cocktail" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="sp-priceitem__main">
              <a class="sp-priceitem__title" href="/booking-calendar/myers-cocktail">Myers' Cocktail</a>
              <p class="sp-priceitem__sub">500ml. The classic wellness drip.</p>
              <a class="sp-priceitem__readmore" href="/service-page/myers-cocktail">Read More</a>
            </div>
            <div class="sp-priceitem__price">$200</div>
            <a class="sp-btn sp-btn--gold sp-priceitem__cta" href="/booking-calendar/myers-cocktail">Request to Book</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-testimonial" aria-label="What Our Clients Say">
      <img class="sp-testimonial__bg" src="/images/30cfb9e87c60.png" alt="" width="1440" height="626" loading="lazy" />
      <div class="sp-testimonial__overlay"></div>
      <div class="sp-container sp-testimonial__inner">
        <h2 class="sp-script-title sp-script-title--light" style="margin-bottom:2rem;">What Our <em>Clients</em> Say</h2>
        <blockquote class="sp-quote">
          <span class="sp-quote__mark">&ldquo;</span>
          Jennifer is amazing. Her aura and energy makes you feel welcomed and comfortable. Love our sessions! And my girl Rose Marie, the receptionist, is just lovely! I always leave with great joy after seeing them.
          <cite>Alexa C.</cite>
        </blockquote>
        <img src="/images/5be44787b3a9.png" alt="5 Star Google Reviews" width="143" height="74" loading="lazy" style="margin-top:1.75rem;" />
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-faq" aria-label="Frequently asked questions">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div class="sp-faq__card">
          <div class="sp-faq__head"><h2 class="sp-faq__title">Frequently asked questions</h2></div>
          <div class="sp-faq__list">
            <details class="sp-faq__item" open>
              <summary>What conditions does the Myers' Cocktail help with?</summary>
              <div class="sp-faq__answer"><p>Clinically, Myers' Cocktail has been shown to be beneficial for fatigue, fibromyalgia, migraines, depression, seasonal allergic rhinitis, acute respiratory infections, asthma attacks, and general wellness enhancement. It's one of the most versatile and well-researched IV treatments available.</p></div>
            </details>
            <details class="sp-faq__item">
              <summary>How often should I get the Myers' Cocktail?</summary>
              <div class="sp-faq__answer"><p>For acute conditions, weekly treatments for 4-8 weeks are often recommended. For general wellness maintenance, monthly infusions help most clients maintain consistent energy levels and overall well-being year-round.</p></div>
            </details>
            <details class="sp-faq__item">
              <summary>Is the Myers' Cocktail safe?</summary>
              <div class="sp-faq__answer"><p>Yes. The Myers' Cocktail has an excellent safety record with decades of clinical use. It contains only natural vitamins and minerals in therapeutic doses. Our team will review your health history before treatment to ensure it's appropriate for you.</p></div>
            </details>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-cta" aria-label="Experience the Original Wellness Drip">
      <div class="sp-container sp-cta__grid">
        <div class="sp-cta__copy">
          <h2 class="sp-cta__title">Experience the Original Wellness Drip</h2>
          <p class="sp-cta__sub">Menon Medispa Millburn NJ</p>
          <p>Schedule your Myers' Cocktail IV therapy at Menon Medispa in Millburn, NJ and experience the gold standard of vitamin infusion therapy.</p>
          <a class="sp-btn sp-btn--gold" href="/consultation">Schedule Free Consultation</a>
        </div>
        <div class="sp-cta__media">
          <img src="/images/b1a819f35921.webp" alt="Menon Office Staff" width="431" height="560" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</BaseLayout>
